        {
            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "I think it's a bad idea, in fact I think the suggested mapping in the help should come with a warning that doing so will prevent one from using Esc with terminal for any other use. for example, if you are using FZF while remapping Esc in terminal, you won't be able to close the `:Files` window by Esc, it will switch to normal mode instead.",
            "created_at": "2021-09-11T09:38:35Z",
            "html_url": "https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/7648#issuecomment-917376461",
